      "docs": "Requires `HistoryCopy` keys in the app-owned `useSharedComponentCopy` hook (including `historyDetailShow(count)`/`historyDetailHide`). Pass `employeeHref={(id) => showEmployee(id).url}` to link viewable causers to their detail page — registry files never import app Wayfinder routes; omit it to render every causer as plain text. Timestamps and values arrive server-formatted (no client date formatting).",
